data.description: Welcome Home! Walking in to this traditional home you will not want to leave; updated kitchen, bathrooms and so much more! Hardwood floors, two wood fireplaces, large dining area and living room. There are 3 bedrooms on the main floor with another bedroom and two family room areas downstairs to include a pool table. Plenty of storage in the laundry room could even be used as a workshop area. The outside is fenced with a beautiful deck and plenty of yard and trees to enjoy while entertaining or just relaxing. All located close to schools and parks in an very quiet neighborhood. Call for your viewing today.
